Text:
Now I understand why I had trouble finding the show: it's a horrible show. Video quality is fine, but I'll never watch all these. It's a bad (really bad) reality show that just happens to take place in a kitchen. 

If you're at all interested in cooking, watch Masterchef Australia, instead.

Not at all accurate review! Your opinion is WRONG! :) Didn't expect to enjoy this show as much as I do, but these copies are terrible... there's a HUMMMM in the background of each episode! Sadly, they are the only copies around!

The Humming sound was really getting on my nerves. If these weren't episodes that you made then it's who ever you got it from that's a real idiot cause a entire season with this damn humming. But as you said you can't find any of these so.
